     <div class="date"> 
      <h1>784 险恶用心</h1> 
      <div class="info">
       <span>作者：且听沧海</span>
       <a href="/txt17273/" title="返回《开艘航母去抗日》介绍页" id="book17273">开艘航母去抗日</a> 本章字节数:5058724
       <script type="text/javascript">article_nav('17273','11937329');</script> 
       <a href="http://www.80txt.com/txtxz/17273.html" class="txt" id="down17273">开艘航母去抗日txt下载</a>
